    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Push a Block is a puzzle game where you need to arrange the blocks on stage to reach the end. You can only move the blocks by moving into them, but if there is another block behind it, or something else doesn't let you move it, you'll climb it</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172350/extras/ec60c7fe0c08152cd4d9812284c3d159.poster.avif?t=1745875513\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172350/extras/ec60c7fe0c08152cd4d9812284c3d159.webm?t=1745875513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172350/extras/ec60c7fe0c08152cd4d9812284c3d159.mp4?t=1745875513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has a very simple control, but will slowly start presenting new mechanics which will make you really have to think to reach the end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172350/extras/f2ad47c426ee9e1f48a43b3898b645db.poster.avif?t=1745875513\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172350/extras/f2ad47c426ee9e1f48a43b3898b645db.webm?t=1745875513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172350/extras/f2ad47c426ee9e1f48a43b3898b645db.mp4?t=1745875513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress in the game new enviroments will appear, each presenting it's new mechanic that will add to the stages difficulty and complexity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172350/extras/aeda76b6e0ce52de4a57f13d91fe3726.poster.avif?t=1745875513\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172350/extras/aeda76b6e0ce52de4a57f13d91fe3726.webm?t=1745875513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2172350/extras/aeda76b6e0ce52de4a57f13d91fe3726.mp4?t=1745875513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
